Training data

The training dataset (`OpenxAILabs/nix-reviewer-training` on Hugging Face) was
generated by synthesizing Nix configurations exhibiting known failure patterns
and running each through the Nix evaluator to obtain ground-truth error
messages. Pattern selection was informed by qualitative analysis of publicly
available community discussions; no verbatim forum content, quoted code, or
attributed text appears in the dataset.
